<item>
            <title>[WICKET-4063] Theading issue in AsynchronousDataStore causes OutOfMemory exception</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-4063</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Considering below time sequence:&lt;br/&gt;
1. &quot;entries.offer&quot; is called during &quot;storeData&quot;. &lt;br/&gt;
2. page saving thread comes in, and poll the entry. Then &quot;entryMap.remove&quot; is called. Nothing will be removed since entry has not been added to entryMap yet. &lt;br/&gt;
3. &quot;entryMap.put&quot; is called during &quot;storeData&quot;. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The result is that entries in &quot;entryMap&quot; may never be removed, and the entryMap can increase infinitely. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
